            "nethysUrl": "https://2e.aonprd.com/Monsters.aspx?ID=787",
            "recallKnowledgeText": "Recall Knowledge - Animal : DC 22<br />Recall Knowledge - Undead : DC 22",
            "sidebarText": "<h3 class=\"title\"><img alt=\"Sidebar - Additional Lore\" title=\"Sidebar - Additional Lore\" style=\"height:20px; padding:2px 10px 0px 2px\" src=\"Images\\Icons\\Sidebar_2_AdditionalLore.png\"> Exceptions to Evil</h3>While most undead are evil, revenants are not&#x2014;these unusual stalkers rise not out of a sense of cruelty or hatred of the living, but spontaneously from the need for vengeance following a deep betrayal. One can avoid a revenant&apos;s wrath by simply getting out of its way&#x2014;unless you happen to be its reason for unlife!",
            "source": {
